Here is an even smaller example:

#!/usr/bin/python3

import tensorflow as tf
from tensorflow.python import debug as tf_debug

def problem_op():
    q = tf.FIFOQueue(1, [ tf.string ])
    return q.enqueue([ "hello" ])

sess = tf_debug.LocalCLIDebugWrapperSession(tf.Session())
sess.run(problem_op())

It is specifically the enqueue operation that can't be stepped over.
